Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.79,0:01:03.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:03.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.04,0:01:05.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要去购物了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.04,0:01:05.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm off to go shopping
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么鬼东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.47,0:01:21.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.47,0:01:21.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Over here
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.89,0:01:24.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.89,0:01:24.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.14,0:01:25.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有货吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.14,0:01:25.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you got the goods?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.52,0:01:26.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.52,0:01:26.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.73,0:01:28.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我言必信行必果
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.73,0:01:28.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I always deliver
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.03,0:01:35.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很高兴能跟你做生意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.03,0:01:35.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pleasure doing business with you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.45,0:01:38.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也一样  见不得人的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.45,0:01:38.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Likewise, my shady friend
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.20,0:01:39.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那下次同一时间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:39.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So same time next--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:44.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(622,426)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.33,0:01:50.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是来抢秘方的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:50.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm here for the formula
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.13,0:01:52.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我交出来  才不会有人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.13,0:01:52.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hand it over, and nobody gets--
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.63,0:01:58.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像踩到什么恶心的东西上面了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:01:58.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I seem to have stepped in some revolting substance
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.34,0:01:59.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.34,0:01:59.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No matter
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.23,0:02:12.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亲爱的  我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:12.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Honey, I'm home
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.15,0:02:15.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天抢秘方一定很艰难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.15,0:02:15.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tough day at work, dear?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.03,0:02:15.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:15.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.15,0:02:18.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家又踩到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:18.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everybody stepped on me again
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.24,0:02:20.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.24,0:02:20.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I know
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.11,0:02:22.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有什么能让我的小家伙振作起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.11,0:02:22.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what'll cheer up my little man
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.70,0:02:25.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起借舞消愁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:25.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's dance those blues away
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.08,0:02:26.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:26.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:28.54,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(936,562)}舞厅
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.16,0:02:29.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:29.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.21,0:02:30.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳起来  谢尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:30.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go, Sheldon
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.42,0:02:33.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得对  凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.42,0:02:33.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You were right, Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.17,0:02:35.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经感觉好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:35.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel better already
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.96,0:02:38.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我特想狂舞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:38.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got boogie fever
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.18,0:02:43.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,婚礼那晚后就再也没这么跳过舞了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:43.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We haven't danced like this since our wedding night
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.81,0:02:50.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:50.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.10,0:02:51.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:51.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.06,0:02:53.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.06,0:02:53.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pardon me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.73,0:02:54.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:54.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pardon me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.19,0:02:55.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:55.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.07,0:02:58.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板  在吗甜心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:58.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton, are you there, sweetie?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.11,0:02:58.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:02:58.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.74,0:03:00.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:00.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.41,0:03:03.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在这啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:03.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you are
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.74,0:03:05.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至少一小部分在这
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:05.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At least part of you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.33,0:03:06.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:06.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.41,0:03:09.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也不想任人践踏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:09.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not getting stepped on anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.83,0:03:11.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带我去实验室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:11.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take me to my lab
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.29,0:03:12.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:12.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.54,0:03:15.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过还是先找你剩下的部分比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:15.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But let's find the rest of you first
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.56,0:03:28.22,标准-Chi,,700,0,0,,脚部威慑装置1.1版本
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.56,0:03:28.22,标准-Eng,,700,0,0,,Foot Deterrent, Version 1.1
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.22,0:03:29.52,标准-Chi,,700,0,0,,开始测试
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:29.52,标准-Eng,,700,0,0,,commence test
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.23,0:03:34.52,标准-Chi,,700,0,0,,还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:34.52,标准-Eng,,700,0,0,,Not quite there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:36.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,很多版本之后
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.53,0:03:40.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脚部威慑装置  激光版
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:40.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Foot Deterrent, laser thingy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.53,0:03:43.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该能过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:43.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Might as well get this over with
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.74,0:03:47.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:47.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.95,0:03:49.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:49.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.12,0:03:50.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我天下无敌了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:50.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm invincible
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.80,0:04:06.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  现在来做实地测试
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:06.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, time for a field test
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.89,0:04:10.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒数三二一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:10.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in T-minus 3, 2, 1
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.06,0:04:17.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的脚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:17.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My foot
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.44,0:04:24.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我接招  高高在上臭火腿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:24.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take that, you high-stepping ham
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.70,0:04:27.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:27.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.99,0:04:30.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来让那双大铁脚再也没法瞎踩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:30.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to stop those big metal stompers
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.47,0:04:45.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板  你到底在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:45.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton, what in tarnation are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.34,0:04:47.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差点就把我爪子给烤了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:47.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You almost barbecued my dang paw
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.55,0:04:49.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就是重点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:49.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was the point
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.76,0:04:53.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过  你刚刚那堆嗨呀的是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:53.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But hey, what was that "hiyah" stuff you just did?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.56,0:04:56.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是一点传统防身术罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:56.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that was just good, old-fashioned self-defense
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.65,0:04:58.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也就是  空手道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:58.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, karate
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.40,0:05:02.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看样子你也很需要学防身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:02.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like you could use a little self-defense too
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.19,0:05:03.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不然你就来我树屋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:03.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you swing by my dome
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.82,0:05:05.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来给你露两手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:05.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I can show you some moves?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.82,0:05:08.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能让别人别踩我就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:08.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anything to stop the stomping
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.00,0:05:20.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板  出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:20.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, Plankton, come on out
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.71,0:05:25.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我显得道袍好看多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:25.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I make this gi look good
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.42,0:05:27.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,向你的师傅鞠躬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:27.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now bow to your sensei
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.97,0:05:30.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板绝不向别人鞠躬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:30.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton bows to no one
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.35,0:05:33.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:33.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.18,0:05:36.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在可以开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:36.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now we may begin
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.10,0:05:40.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先来评估你当前的防身水平
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:40.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We must first gauge your current level of self-defense
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.27,0:05:41.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:41.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Think fast
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.57,0:05:42.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:42.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Think what?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.15,0:05:46.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于知道为什么这个叫运动鞋了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:46.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I know why they call it a sneaker
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:46.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1226,920)}偷 袭
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.95,0:05:50.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,换个力度小一点的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:50.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe something a little gentler
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.49,0:05:54.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不会跟你一样空翻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:54.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't flip like you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:54.29,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1192,920)}拖
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.29,0:05:55.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只会砸锅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:55.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only flop
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:55.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1028,920)}鞋
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.87,0:05:56.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:56.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.91,0:05:59.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就换这双
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:59.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How 'bout these?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.96,0:06:05.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来你缺乏基础
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:05.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Seems like you lack the fundamentals
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.55,0:06:09.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得给你做点基础训练
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:09.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What you need is some basic training
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.09,0:06:12.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好好  长毛的小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:12.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okey-dokey, furry lady
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.47,0:06:51.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然你已经掌握基础了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:51.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now that you've mastered the basics
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.76,0:06:55.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想必你已经准备好来真人快打了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:55.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I reckon you're ready to spar with a real partner
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:55.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(836,310)}婴儿鞋
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.93,0:06:57.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:57.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.27,0:06:58.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:58.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.73,0:06:59.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你别怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:06:59.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.94,0:07:01.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会放水的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:01.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll go easy on ya
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.56,0:07:03.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡沫陪练靴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:03.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Foam sparring boots
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.86,0:07:06.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可不一定会手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:06.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't promise I'll do the same
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.48,0:07:08.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,向对手鞠躬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:08.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bow to your opponents
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.45,0:07:11.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开打
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:11.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now fight
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.25,0:07:20.75,标准-Chi,,600,0,0,,表现很好  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:20.75,标准-Eng,,600,0,0,,That was pretty good, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.75,0:07:22.58,标准-Chi,,600,0,0,,但别忘了时刻保持警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:22.58,标准-Eng,,600,0,0,,But remember to keep your guard up
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.58,0:07:24.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:24.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's no use
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.46,0:07:27.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我太小了  很难不任人践踏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:27.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm just too small to avoid being stepped on
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.38,0:07:30.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是在空手道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:30.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But in karate
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.97,0:07:34.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你最大的弱点也可能会是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:34.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your greatest weakness may also be
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.26,0:07:36.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你最强的长处
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:36.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your greatest strength
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.22,0:07:37.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:37.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.01,0:07:40.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是在现实道  根本不可能有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:40.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But in "rea-li-tay," that doesn't make any sense
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.89,0:07:42.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,由我来为你演示
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:42.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Allow me to demonstrate
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.98,0:07:46.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  给我回旋踢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:46.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, give me the old roundhouse
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.94,0:07:49.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以借对手的冲击力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:49.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your opponent's momentum can be used--
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.28,0:07:53.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加以反击  无论你有多大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:53.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,--against them, no matter your size
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.66,0:07:54.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:54.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You OK, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.03,0:07:57.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要能鞠躬的话  早就鞠了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:57.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I would bow to you If I could
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.95,0:08:01.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:01.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was incredible
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.87,0:08:04.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来试试
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:04.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me try
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.29,0:08:06.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让技法浮现在脑海中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:06.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Visualize the technique
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.21,0:08:09.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一抓一转  剩下的全部交给重力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:09.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grab, twist, and let gravity do the rest
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.67,0:08:10.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:10.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shut up
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.80,0:08:12.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你害我分心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:12.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're distracting me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.85,0:08:24.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:24.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I did it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.40,0:08:26.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当面打脸了  臭脚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:26.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In your face, feet
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.65,0:08:29.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恭喜你  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:29.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.69,0:08:31.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但要记住  这种技法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:31.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But remember, this technique
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.49,0:08:34.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只能用来自卫  不能图谋不轨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:34.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is to be used strictly for self-defense
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.95,0:08:37.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然  珊迪师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:37.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course, Sensei Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.99,0:08:38.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,眨眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:38.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wink
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.20,0:08:40.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再也不见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:40.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Buh-bye
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.96,0:08:46.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  你能送我去医院吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:46.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, could you give me a ride to the hospital?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.13,0:08:48.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:48.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.96,0:08:52.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  谁想来打架
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:52.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, who's looking to rumble?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.67,0:08:54.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:54.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.31,0:09:04.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么无法解释的自然之力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:04.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What unexplained force of nature?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.40,0:09:10.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我感觉好强大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:10.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel so powerful
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.36,0:09:14.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,忍不住要使出这身力量干坏事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:14.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I can't help but use that power for evil
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:18.91,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(644,434)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.62,0:09:21.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:21.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Krabsy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.87,0:09:25.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:25.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm home
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.76,0:09:34.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在没人能阻止我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.76,0:09:34.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one can stop me now
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.17,0:09:38.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘密配方就要归我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:38.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That secret formula will be mine
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.64,0:09:43.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:43.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.77,0:09:45.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么是痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:45.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, not Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.15,0:09:51.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:51.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I made it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.45,0:09:58.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,忍者保安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:58.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Security ninjas?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.70,0:10:00.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老螃蟹考虑得还真周到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:00.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabs thinks of everything
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.28,0:10:03.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.28,0:10:03.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bring it on
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.65,0:10:30.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,敲敲门
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:30.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Knock, knock
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.44,0:10:33.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:33.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.65,0:10:36.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是怎么绕过我的忍者保安的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:36.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How did you get past me security ninjas?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.49,0:10:38.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用空手道绕过的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:38.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With the art of karate
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.99,0:10:40.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然我现在会防身了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:40.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now that I can defend myself
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.87,0:10:43.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的双脚要完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.87,0:10:43.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your feet are all doomed
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.46,0:10:49.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下你绝对笑不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:49.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You won't be laughing
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.79,0:10:53.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我马上就要使出终极踩脚终结神功
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.79,0:10:53.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,once I use my ultimate foot-stomping finisher
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.92,0:10:57.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你说个坏消息  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:57.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bad news for you, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.26,0:10:59.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没有脚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:59.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't have any feet
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.88,0:11:01.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:01.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You what?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.51,0:11:05.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是倒霉透了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:05.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just my luck, I guess
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.14,0:11:11.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,任人践踏的失败滋味是不是很熟悉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:11.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The old familiar sting of "de-feet," aye?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:17.28,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1582,462)}医院
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:17.28,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(864,546)}急诊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.03,0:11:20.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再过六到八个星期
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:20.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Six to eight weeks
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.36,0:11:22.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就又能去蟹堡王发动进攻了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:22.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before I can attack the Krusty Krab again
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.32,0:11:24.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:24.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, well
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.03,0:11:26.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码我再也不用做牵引治疗了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:26.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At least I'm not in traction anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.66,0:11:28.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:28.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.79,0:11:30.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要再等六到八个星期
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:30.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only six to eight weeks
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.25,0:11:32.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就又能去蟹堡王上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:32.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before I can work at the Krusty Krab again
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.88,0:11:36.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,空手道真讨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:36.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karate is a pain in the--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:40.55,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H00FFA3&}为泡芙健身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:41.97,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(702,372)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:41.97,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(718,664)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:46.39,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:43.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(632,450)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:43.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(770,648)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:44.89,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(726,542)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:46.39,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(558,546)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:48.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(656,544)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:48.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:49.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1440,718)}欢迎来到酷乐湖
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.61,0:11:57.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:57.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Miss
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.07,0:11:59.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位子占了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:11:59.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is this seat taken?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.07,0:12:01.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在就占了  水手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.07,0:12:01.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is now, Sailor
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.20,0:12:11.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三声铃声
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:11.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Three bells?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.16,0:12:13.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,午餐时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:13.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's lunchtime
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.00,0:12:14.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好弄点吃的来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:14.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Better get some food
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.54,0:12:17.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卖奶酪火锅的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:17.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Fondue Man
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.82,0:12:47.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小费才半毛钱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:47.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A 5 cent tip?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.45,0:12:49.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可真谢谢你了  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:49.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot, Mister
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.54,0:12:52.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奶酪火锅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:52.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fondue
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.71,0:12:55.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最适合海滩约会的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:55.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The perfect food for a beach date
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.88,0:12:59.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:12:59.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.00,0:13:00.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:00.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.92,0:13:01.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:01.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.46,0:13:01.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.46,0:13:01.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.20,0:13:33.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚吃得真爽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:33.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, that was a meal
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.12,0:13:33.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说要不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:33.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you say
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.91,0:13:36.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下酷乐湖浪漫游个泳呢  我的甜心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:36.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to a romantic dip in the goo, my sweet?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.08,0:13:40.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我确实挺想洗掉身上沾到的奶酪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:40.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose I could wash off some of this cheese
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.35,0:13:57.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尤金
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:57.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eugene
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.23,0:13:59.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,逆流卷走我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:59.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The undertow's got me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.56,0:14:02.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:02.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:03.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1342,898)}救生员
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.98,0:14:05.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,激流里浮着个大屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:05.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rump in a riptide
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.29,0:14:14.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来救你了  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:14.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gotcha, bro
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.72,0:14:30.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  拉里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:30.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Larry
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.60,0:14:34.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:34.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.26,0:14:34.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:34.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.97,0:14:36.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:36.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.44,0:14:41.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尤金  不必多说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:41.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eugene, don't try to talk
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.90,0:14:43.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我先带你回家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:43.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd better take you home
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.11,0:14:45.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  拉里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:45.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye, Larry
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.11,0:14:48.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再次谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.11,0:14:48.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks again
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.28,0:14:51.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拉里随时出马
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:51.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Larry's always ready to step in
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:15:00.33,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(516,472)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.29,0:15:00.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你说吧  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:00.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.87,0:15:03.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那一吻  那一浪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:03.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that kiss, that wave--
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.42,0:15:05.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就快把我可爱的泡芙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:05.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm losing me sweet Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.59,0:15:09.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,输给一个外壳发亮的小白脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:09.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to a shiny-shelled boy toy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.68,0:15:12.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能是你看错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:12.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe your eyes were confused
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.01,0:15:15.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:15.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.31,0:15:18.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她就爱拉里的肌肉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:18.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She loved Larry's muscles
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.48,0:15:23.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她都烦透了我这奶酪火锅老皮囊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:23.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's sick of this old sack of fondue
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.98,0:15:25.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听着  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:25.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, Mr. K
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.40,0:15:28.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师肯定爱的是你的内在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:28.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Mrs. Puff loves you for who you are
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.74,0:15:30.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而不是你有多少肌肉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:30.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not how many muscles you have
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.28,0:15:32.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:32.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.24,0:15:34.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看好了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:34.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.24,0:15:37.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,衣服里面没晒黑  外壳软弱又无力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:37.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This farmer's tan, this flabby shell
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.45,0:15:39.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要身材没身材
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:39.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so undefined
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.66,0:15:44.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹到中年老吃奶酪火锅  下场就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:44.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See the realities of middle age on an all-fondue diet
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.67,0:15:46.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别看我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:46.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look away
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.71,0:15:51.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是个螃蟹都不应该这副德行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:51.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No crab should look like this
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.47,0:15:57.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没别的选择了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:57.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's only one option, boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.64,0:16:00.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定得在下次约会前练好身材
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.64,0:16:00.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gotta get in shape before me next date
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.48,0:16:02.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:02.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you're gonna help
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:09.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(814,274)}拉里健身房
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.73,0:16:08.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那只壮龙虾肯定不认识我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:08.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That crustaceous hunk doesn't know who I am
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.36,0:16:09.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也不知道我干嘛来  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:09.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or why I'm here, boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.65,0:16:14.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.65,0:16:14.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go, go, go
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.53,0:16:15.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:15.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.33,0:16:19.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冲冲冲冲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:19.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go, go, go, go
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.75,0:16:20.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,流汗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:20.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sweat
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.45,0:16:21.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不该来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:21.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This was a mistake
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.46,0:16:22.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弃健身房逃命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:22.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Abandon gym
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.87,0:16:24.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能行的  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:24.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can do this, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.67,0:16:26.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全是为了泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:26.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do it for Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.84,0:16:29.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:29.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.55,0:16:31.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要为泡芙健身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:31.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll do it for Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.59,0:16:37.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临我的健身神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:37.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to my temple of the bods
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.85,0:16:39.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,少给我推销了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:39.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Save the sales pitch
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.01,0:16:39.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:39.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got this
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.10,0:16:47.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你说  那个其实是给
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:47.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, that's actually for--
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.15,0:16:49.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,举重举完了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:49.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finished me reps
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.44,0:16:50.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:50.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.44,0:16:53.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以教你怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:53.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can show you how to--
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.74,0:16:54.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:54.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.03,0:16:54.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,心率上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:54.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got me heart rate up
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.70,0:16:57.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:57.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.03,0:16:58.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没听过那谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.03,0:16:58.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never heard of him
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.21,0:17:06.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一天来一定不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:06.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Must be shy about his first day
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.58,0:17:09.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果你想健身  我很乐意帮你训练
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:09.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you want to work out, I'd be happy to help train you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.05,0:17:15.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  多半确实得来点指导
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:15.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, maybe I could use a few pointers
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.89,0:17:19.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你先试试做点自由重量训练
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:19.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's just try lifting some free weights
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:19.39,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 自由重量：指可以举起并四处移动的\N任何重量的器材，如哑铃 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.39,0:17:21.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拉里你看  我举起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:21.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, Larry, I'm doing it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.48,0:17:27.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:27.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sponge--
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.57,0:17:33.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不许偷自由重量器材  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:33.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No stealing the free weights, bro
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.82,0:17:36.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是说免费吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:36.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, are they free or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:36.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1024,920)}自 由
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.29,0:17:44.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从来没见过你这么不乐意健身的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:44.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've never met anyone as workout-averse as you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.75,0:17:46.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我真不知道要怎么激励你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:46.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just don't know how to motivate you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.87,0:17:49.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道怎么激励他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:49.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know how to motivate him
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.84,0:17:57.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱  钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:57.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Money, money
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.68,0:18:01.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:01.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Money
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.31,0:18:01.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.31,0:18:01.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Money
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.93,0:18:02.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:02.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Money
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.47,0:18:03.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:03.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Money
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.27,0:18:05.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这办法好  小兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.27,0:18:05.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice trick, little dude
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.14,0:18:06.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:06.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.18,0:18:08.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我骗他吃药才叫好看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:08.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You should see how I get him to take his pills
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.92,0:18:34.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:34.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.76,0:18:36.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,一周后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.67,0:18:37.63,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(556,488)}蒸汽浴室
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.59,0:18:43.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,健身健得真久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:43.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was one heck of a workout
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.22,0:18:47.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看连续健了168小时的身
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.22,0:18:47.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to see what 168 straight hours of exercise
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.60,0:18:49.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,效果变得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:49.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,does to the body
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.82,0:19:01.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事  拉里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.82,0:19:01.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the deal, Larry?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.20,0:19:02.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我怎么没变壮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:02.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why ain't I ripped?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.74,0:19:05.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,健身得健一辈子  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:05.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fitness is a lifelong journey, bro
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.79,0:19:08.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只练一周没法改变体格
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:08.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't change your physique in a week
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.33,0:19:14.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,桑拿房见  兄弟们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:14.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you bros in the sauna
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.51,0:19:22.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没法改变体格是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:22.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one can change their physique, eh?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.95,0:19:45.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  女士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:45.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey there, ma'am
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.78,0:19:47.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这片海滩占了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:47.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is this beach taken?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.70,0:19:49.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:49.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.58,0:19:53.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尤金  你身材真好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:53.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eugene, you're so well-defined
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.21,0:19:55.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尤金
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:55.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eugene?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.13,0:19:56.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:56.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.21,0:19:57.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:19:57.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.88,0:19:58.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:19:58.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take a look
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.34,0:20:01.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是长肌肉  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:01.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These are called gains, people
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.72,0:20:03.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:03.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.02,0:20:18.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肌肉真棒  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:18.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice pecs, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.36,0:20:20.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:20.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We love you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.40,0:20:21.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:21.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We love you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.99,0:20:24.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全世界最壮的螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.99,0:20:24.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Strongest crab in the world
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.61,0:20:26.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天不怕地不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.61,0:20:26.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I fear no man
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.28,0:20:28.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:28.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.87,0:20:31.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拉里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.87,0:20:31.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Larry?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:31.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1624,816)}蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:33.54,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1586,244)}贻贝海滩
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.37,0:20:35.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要把你砸出我的壳  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:35.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to crack you right out of my shell, bro
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.21,0:20:38.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  真帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:38.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, looking good
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.01,0:20:42.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是拉里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:42.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Was that Larry?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.80,0:20:45.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他一定有好几分钟没健身了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:45.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He must have stopped working out for a few minutes
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.73,0:20:52.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奶酪火锅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.73,0:20:52.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fondue?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.93,0:20:54.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在海滩上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.93,0:20:54.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At the beach?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.70,0:21:06.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拉里有危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:06.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Larry's in trouble
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.16,0:21:07.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来个谁快救救他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:07.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Someone save him
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.16,0:21:09.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁来给救生员救生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:09.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who will lifeguard the lifeguards?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.29,0:21:13.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卖奶酪火锅的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.29,0:21:13.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fondue Man
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.46,0:21:16.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:16.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.12,0:21:16.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:16.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.76,0:21:22.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:22.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.81,0:21:37.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.81,0:21:37.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.36,0:21:41.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  我把场面救回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.36,0:21:41.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right, saving the day over here
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.32,0:21:43.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你现在觉得我怎么样  阿芙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:43.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you think of me now, Puffykins?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.07,0:21:46.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你家老螃蟹可真是个英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:46.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your old Krabsy is quite the hero
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.66,0:21:49.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:49.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Puh-lease
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.78,0:21:53.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可不喜欢只顾自己的肌肉男
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.78,0:21:53.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not into muscle-bound, self-centered jerks
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.54,0:21:55.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.54,0:21:55.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.33,0:21:58.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱的男生就该稍微轻软一点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:58.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I like my boys a little soft around the edges
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.50,0:22:04.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我跟拉里明天要来海滩约会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:04.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's why Larry and I have a beach date tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.01,0:22:09.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拉里喜欢海滩约会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.01,0:22:09.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Larry loves beach dates
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.22,0:22:10.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海滩约会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.22,0:22:10.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Beach date?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.47,0:22:11.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.47,0:22:11.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.26,0:22:13.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我闹着玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.26,0:22:13.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was kidding
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.01,0:22:15.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这身肌肉都是幌子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.01,0:22:15.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The muscles were just a ruse
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.14,0:22:16.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.14,0:22:16.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Puffy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.02,0:22:20.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:20.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.94,0:22:22.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.94,0:22:22.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come back
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.02,0:22:24.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,阿芙  我可软了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.02,0:22:24.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Puffykins, I'm soft
